# Git LFS managed assets
#
# Keep source text in normal Git. Put generated prototypes, media,
# design exports, archives, and other large binary assets in LFS.

# Root-level standalone prototypes and exported mockups.
/*.html filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text

# Images and design files.
*.png filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.jpg filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
